Invocation Name: elección nacional
des: Eleccion Nacional provides essential electoral information to citizens, including how to register to vote, requirements for becoming a candidate, where to find your polling station, and real-time updates on election results. This skill is designed to support users in navigating the electoral process efficiently, with easy access to FAQs, voting safety measures, and more. Available 24/7, Eleccion Nacional offers essential services in a user-friendly interface, ensuring you are always informed.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
